    "During this time period, the earliest related research appeared in 2005.",
    "The distribution of the publications from 2005 to 2022 is shown in Fig. 1.",
    "Figure 1 illustrates the number of publications in the realm of Chinese sentiment analysis spanning the years 2005 to 2022.",
    "Evidently, the publication count follows an exponential growth trajectory over time.",
    "The data demonstrates a notable peak in 2016, followed by a minor decline and a subsequent peak in 2018."
